<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Project Proposal</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts for premium typography -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @page {
            size: A4;
            margin: 20mm 20mm 20mm 20mm;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #334155;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        /* Cover Page styling */
        .cover-page {
            height: 100%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 40px 0;
            page-break-after: always;
        }

        .cover-accent {
            width: 80px;
            height: 6px;
            background-color: #6366f1; /* Indigo */
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .cover-title {
            font-size: 28pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f172a;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        }

        .cover-subtitle {
            font-size: 14pt;
            color: #6366f1;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 0 0 40px 0;
        }

        .cover-details {
            margin-top: 100px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-top: 30px;
        }

        .details-grid {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        .details-col p {
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
        }

        /* Standard Header */
        .doc-header {
            border-bottom: 3px solid #6366f1;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .doc-title-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-end;
        }

        .doc-title {
            font-size: 20pt;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin: 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .doc-subtitle-small {
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #6366f1;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 5px 0 0 0;
        }

        /* Sections */
        h2 {
            font-size: 13pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin-top: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-bottom: 6px;
            page-break-after: avoid;
        }

        h3 {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6366f1;
            margin-top: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        /* Two Column Box Layout */
        .grid-box {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .box-item {
            width: 48%;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        .box-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0f172a;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 10.5pt;
        }

        .box-desc {
            font-size: 9.5pt;
            color: #475569;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* Timeline / Phases */
        .timeline-container {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .phase-item {
            border-left: 2px solid #6366f1;
            padding-left: 15px;
            margin-left: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            position: relative;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }

        .phase-item::before {
            content: '';
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            background-color: #6366f1;
            border-radius: 50%;
            position: absolute;
            left: -6px;
            top: 5px;
        }

        .phase-item:last-child {
            padding-bottom: 0;
        }

        .phase-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: baseline;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }

        .phase-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0f172a;
            font-size: 10.5pt;
        }

        .phase-duration {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #6366f1;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .phase-desc {
            font-size: 9.5pt;
            color: #475569;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* Pricing Table */
        .price-table {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .price-table th {
            background-color: #6366f1;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: left;
            padding: 10px 12px;
            font-size: 9.5pt;
        }

        .price-table td {
            padding: 10px 12px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 9.5pt;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .price-table tr:nth-child(even) td {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }

        .price-table td.amount {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0f172a;
        }

        .why-us-list {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .why-us-list li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .next-steps-box {
            background-color: #e0e7ff;
            border: 1px solid #c7d2fe;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .next-steps-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #3730a3;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }

        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Cover Page -->
    <div class="cover-page">
        <div>
            <div class="cover-accent"></div>
            <h1 class="cover-title">PROJECT PROPOSAL</h1>
            <p class="cover-subtitle">Tailored Software Engineering & Integration Plan</p>
            <p style="font-size: 11pt; color: #475569; max-width: 80%;">A comprehensive proposal detailing the problem analysis, strategic solution architecture, estimated project timeline, and pricing tiers prepared specifically for <%= client.name %>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="cover-details">
            <div class="details-grid">
                <div class="details-col">
                    <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 8.5pt; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">PREPARED FOR</p>
                    <p><strong><%= client.name %></strong></p>
                    <p><%= client.company || 'Client Organization' %></p>
                    <p><%= client.email %></p>
                </div>
                <div class="details-col" style="text-align: right;">
                    <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 8.5pt; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">PREPARED BY</p>
                    <p><strong><%= developer.name %></strong></p>
                    <p><%= developer.email %></p>
                    <p><%= developer.website || '' %></p>
                    <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= date %> | <strong>Valid Until:</strong> <%= validUntil || '30 days from date' %></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content Header -->
    <div class="doc-header">
        <div class="doc-title-container">
            <div>
                <h1 class="doc-title">Project Overview</h1>
                <div class="doc-subtitle-small">Proposal Summary & Solution Architecture</div>
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 9pt; color: #64748b; text-align: right;">
                <strong>Project:</strong> <%= project.name %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Executive Summary</h2>
    <div class="grid-box">
        <div class="box-item">
            <div class="box-title">The Challenge / Problem</div>
            <div class="box-desc"><%= problem %></div>
        </div>
        <div class="box-item">
            <div class="box-title">Our Strategic Solution</div>
            <div class="box-desc"><%= solution %></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <h2>2. Proposed Timeline & Project Phases</h2>
    <p>To ensure high quality and alignment, we propose dividing the development cycle into structured phases. Each phase concludes with client review and milestone approval:</p>
    
    <div class="timeline-container">
        <% if (typeof phases !== 'undefined' && phases && phases.length > 0) { %>
            <% phases.forEach(function(phase) { %>
                <div class="phase-item">
                    <div class="phase-header">
                        <span class="phase-title"><%= phase.name %></span>
                        <span class="phase-duration"><%= phase.duration %></span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="phase-desc"><%= phase.description %></p>
                </div>
            <% }); %>
        <% } else { %>
            <div class="phase-item">
                <div class="phase-header">
                    <span class="phase-title">Phase 1: Discovery & Architecture</span>
                    <span class="phase-duration">1-2 Weeks</span>
                </div>
                <p class="phase-desc">Wireframing, API design, database schema planning, and environment setups.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="phase-item">
                <div class="phase-header">
                    <span class="phase-title">Phase 2: Core Sprint Development</span>
                    <span class="phase-duration">4-6 Weeks</span>
                </div>
                <p class="phase-desc">Frontend construction, API integrations, authentication setup, and core database interactions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="phase-item">
                <div class="phase-header">
                    <span class="phase-title">Phase 3: Quality Assurance & Testing</span>
                    <span class="phase-duration">1-2 Weeks</span>
                </div>
                <p class="phase-desc">Cross-browser visual checks, performance optimizations, end-to-end user testing, and bug resolutions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="phase-item">
                <div class="phase-header">
                    <span class="phase-title">Phase 4: Launch & Handover</span>
                    <span class="phase-duration">1 Week</span>
                </div>
                <p class="phase-desc">Production server configurations, domain routing, credentials handover, and support setup.</p>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="page-break"></div>

    <h2>3. Pricing Options & Estimates</h2>
    <p>We propose a transparent pricing model for the project execution. Below are the estimated investments for the scope of work described:</p>
    
    <table class="price-table">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th style="width: 70%;">Deliverable / Package Option</th>
                <th style="width: 30%; text-align: right;">Estimated Investment</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <% if (typeof pricingOptions !== 'undefined' && pricingOptions && pricingOptions.length > 0) { %>
                <% pricingOptions.forEach(function(opt) { %>
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <strong><%= opt.name %></strong><br>
                            <span style="font-size: 8.5pt; color: #64748b;"><%= opt.description %></span>
                        </td>
                        <td class="amount" style="text-align: right;"><%= currency %> <%= opt.amount %></td>
                    </tr>
                <% }); %>
            <% } else { %>
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        <strong>Full-Scale Scope (Fixed Price)</strong><br>
                        <span style="font-size: 8.5pt; color: #64748b;">Includes all features in the SOW, 3 months post-launch support, and deployments.</span>
                    </td>
                    <td class="amount" style="text-align: right;"><%= currency %> <%= pricing.total %></td>
                </tr>
            <% } %>
        </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>4. Why Partner With Us</h2>
    <ul class="why-us-list">
        <% if (typeof whyUs !== 'undefined' && whyUs && whyUs.length > 0) { %>
            <% whyUs.forEach(function(point) { %>
                <li><%= point %></li>
            <% }); %>
        <% } else { %>
            <li><strong>Expert Technical Capability:</strong> Specialized experience in building modern, scalable React/Node.js products that handle high user volumes cleanly.</li>
            <li><strong>Clear & Prompt Communication:</strong> Weekly progress updates via video calls, direct access to the active Git repository, and interactive testing links.</li>
            <li><strong>Security First Approach:</strong> Implementation of OAuth2, secure JWT protocols, data encryption, and proper environmental setups from day one.</li>
        <% } %>
    </ul>

    <div class="next-steps-box">
        <div class="next-steps-title">5. Next Steps to Get Started</div>
        <ol style="margin: 0; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 9.5pt; color: #3730a3;">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 6px;"><strong>Proposal Approval:</strong> Notify the Developer of your package preference and timeline confirmation.</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 6px;"><strong>Contract Execution:</strong> Sign the formal Service Agreement / Contract and finalize the SOW.</li>
            <li><strong>Advance Deposit:</strong> Process the initial <%= currency %> <%= pricing.advance %> advance invoice to trigger project kick-off.</li>
        </ol>
    </div>

</body>

</html>
